summary: Just 2 Save Games (Female and Male) that have the first 2-3 main quests finished just up to the point where you unlock the full Fus Ro Dah shout.
descriptionHtml:
[center]These Saves Provide a Female DragonBorn and a Male Dragonborn Save Game
The first few main quests were completed, and you start as a level 1
When you load these saves you start in riverwood with around 250 gold, the golden claw,Â 
The Complete 'Fus Ro Dah' Shout, 5 Health Potions, and Some letters...I made this for my own personal use, but i figured id uploaded it since i only made it because i couldnt find it on the web...
I restart a lot and the tutorial and first few quests get old after 200+ times doing them

[/center][b][u][i][size=5][center]The mods i used when making the save are:[/center]

[center][color=#ff0000][size=4][b][u]THESE SAVES DO NOT REQUIRE ANY MODS! I USED A FEW MODS WHILE MAKING THEM BUT BEFORE I SAVED I UNINSTALLED THEM!

IT IS A NORMAL SKYRIM SAVE![/u][/b][/size][/color][/center]
